expression = re.compile(rfc._COOKIE_VALUE_REGEX)
good_examples = ['a_cookie_value', '"quoted-(cookie-value)"', '#big_$$_yo!',
    "&that's-how-we-do", 'some-symbols[*+./:<>=?@^_`{|}]~']
for good_example in good_examples:
    self.assertTrue(bool(expression.fullmatch(good_example)), msg=
        "valid cookie value '{v}' did not match regex".format(v=good_example))
